newsitem.title: SINGAPORE: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Oct 17.
newsitem.headline: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Oct 17.

text.p: DELIVERED U.S.$/TONNE) 380 CST 180 CST MDO GAS OIL

COMMENTS - Singapore bunker levels ease late Thursday to end little changed from Wednesday following cargo levels, traders said. A major oil company said prices were wide-ranged with prompt 380-cst supplies loading within the next two days offered at $121.50 per tonne while cargoes loading next week were offered at $124. MDO prices firmed on strong gas oil prices.
